name: CUCUMGECKO
description:
Collaborative piece between Ronald
Ong and CoinGecko. // Meet your
neighbourhood-friendly Gecko, it’s a
gentle reminder for you to look
around, enjoy funny little things in life
and take on a different perspective. //
Proceeds of the auction will be
donated to Mint.af to further support
the NFT space, as well as charities
involved with The Giving Block.
